* Sort the array 
* And select maximum gap of max element - min element
* If difference >= k then only increase answer and make start of another subsequence as ith element.

Time - O(sort)
```
class Solution {

    public int partitionArray(int[] nums, int k) {
        Arrays.sort(nums);
        int c = 1, prev = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {
            if (nums[i] - nums[prev] <= k) continue;
            c++; prev = i;
        }
        return c;
    }
}
```

