I have used sorting and then upper bound function to find the greater element for element.
like int the case 3,6,1,2,5 the sorted one is 1,2,3,5,6 and k is 2 so the upeer bound of a[0](1)+k(2) will be 5 ane then we will decrease the pos by 1 for equal or less elements which is needed.
